 467:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         is conditioned to ADC state:
 468:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC instance must be disabled.
