2261:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         corresponds to literal definitions of driver.
2262:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   The different literal definitions of ADC channels are:
2263:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC internal channel:
2264:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           LL_ADC_CHANNEL_VREFINT, LL_ADC_CHANNEL_TEMPSENSOR, ...
2265:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC external channel (channel connected to a GPIO pin):
2266:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           LL_ADC_CHANNEL_1, LL_ADC_CHANNEL_2, ...
2267:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   The channel parameter must be a value defined from literal
2268:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         definition of a ADC internal channel (LL_ADC_CHANNEL_VREFINT,
2269:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         LL_ADC_CHANNEL_TEMPSENSOR, ...),
2270:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC external channel (LL_ADC_CHANNEL_1, LL_ADC_CHANNEL_2, ...),
2271:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         must not be a value from functions where a channel number is
2272:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         returned from ADC registers,
