2901:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         VrefInt corresponds to a resolution of 12 bits,
2902:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         this is the recommended ADC resolution to convert voltage of
2903:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         internal voltage reference VrefInt.
