2923:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
2924:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Helper macro to calculate the temperature (unit: degree Celsius)
2925:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         from ADC conversion data of internal temperature sensor.
2926:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Computation is using temperature sensor calibration values
2927:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         stored in system memory for each device during production.
2928:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Calculation formula:
2929:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Temperature = ((TS_ADC_DATA - TS_CAL1)
2930:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                           * (TS_CAL2_TEMP - TS_CAL1_TEMP))
2931:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                         / (TS_CAL2 - TS_CAL1) + TS_CAL1_TEMP
2932:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           with TS_ADC_DATA = temperature sensor raw data measured by ADC
2933:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                Avg_Slope = (TS_CAL2 - TS_CAL1)
2934:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            / (TS_CAL2_TEMP - TS_CAL1_TEMP)
2935:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_CAL1   = equivalent TS_ADC_DATA at temperature
2936:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            TEMP_DEGC_CAL1 (calibrated in factory)
ARM GAS  C:\msys64\tmp\cc6t36jz.s 			page 53


2937:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_CAL2   = equivalent TS_ADC_DATA at temperature
2938:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            TEMP_DEGC_CAL2 (calibrated in factory)
2939:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Caution: Calculation relevancy under reserve that calibration
2940:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  parameters are correct (address and data).
2941:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  To calculate temperature using temperature sensor
2942:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  datasheet typical values (generic values less, therefore
2943:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  less accurate than calibrated values),
2944:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  use helper macro @ref __LL_ADC_CALC_TEMPERATURE_TYP_PARAMS().
2945:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   As calculation input, the analog reference voltage (Vref+) must be
2946:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         defined as it impacts the ADC LSB equivalent voltage.
2947:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Analog reference voltage (Vref+) must be either known from
