4021:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             scan direction is forward (from rank 1 to rank n).
4022:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Sequencer ranks are selected using
4023:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           function "LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerRanks()".
