4977:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
4978:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC group injected conversion trigger:
4979:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         independent or from ADC group regular.
4980:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   This mode can be used to extend number of data registers
4981:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         updated after one ADC conversion trigger and with data
4982:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         permanently kept (not erased by successive conversions of scan of
4983:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC sequencer ranks), up to 5 data registers:
4984:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         1 data register on ADC group regular, 4 data registers
4985:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on ADC group injected.
4986:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   If ADC group injected injected trigger source is set to an
4987:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         external trigger, this feature must be must be set to
4988:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         independent trigger.
4989:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC group injected automatic trigger is compliant only with
4990:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         group injected trigger source set to SW start, without any
4991:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         further action on  ADC group injected conversion start or stop:
4992:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         in this case, ADC group injected is controlled only
4993:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         from ADC group regular.
4994:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   It is not possible to enable both ADC group injected
4995:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         auto-injected mode and sequencer discontinuous mode.
4996:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
4997:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
4998:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be disabled or enabled without conversion on going
4999:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on either groups regular or injected.
