5837:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           of literals LL_ADC_CHANNEL_x. Therefore, it has to be compared
5838:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           with parts of literals LL_ADC_CHANNEL_x or using
5839:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           helper macro @ref __LL_ADC_CHANNEL_TO_DECIMAL_NB().
5840:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Then the selected literal LL_ADC_CHANNEL_x can be used
5841:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           as parameter for another function.
5842:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - To get the channel number in decimal format:
5843:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           process the returned value with the helper macro
5844:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           @ref __LL_ADC_CHANNEL_TO_DECIMAL_NB().
5845:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Applicable only when the analog watchdog is set to monitor
5846:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           one channel.
5847:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, there are 2 kinds of analog watchdog
5848:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         instance:
5849:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - AWD standard (instance AWD1):
5850:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - channels monitored: can monitor 1 channel or all channels.
5851:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - groups monitored: ADC groups regular and-or injected.
5852:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - resolution: resolution is not limited (corresponds to
5853:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             ADC resolution configured).
5854:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - AWD flexible (instances AWD2, AWD3):
ARM GAS  C:\msys64\tmp\cc6t36jz.s 			page 109


5855:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - channels monitored: flexible on channels monitored, selection is
5856:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             channel wise, from from 1 to all channels.
5857:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             Specificity of this analog watchdog: Multiple channels can
5858:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             be selected. For example:
5859:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             (LL_ADC_AWD_CHANNEL4_REG_INJ | LL_ADC_AWD_CHANNEL5_REG_INJ | ...)
5860:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - groups monitored: not selection possible (monitoring on both
5861:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             groups regular and injected).
5862:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             Channels selected are monitored on groups regular and injected:
5863:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             LL_ADC_AWD_CHANNELxx_REG_INJ (do not use parameters
5864:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             LL_ADC_AWD_CHANNELxx_REG and LL_ADC_AWD_CHANNELxx_INJ)
5865:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - resolution: resolution is limited to 8 bits: if ADC resolution is
5866:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             12 bits the 4 LSB are ignored, if ADC resolution is 10 bits
5867:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             the 2 LSB are ignored.
5868:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
