6219:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC oversampling scope: ADC groups regular and-or injected
6220:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (availability of ADC group injected depends on STM32 series).
6221:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   If both groups regular and injected are selected,
