7067:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, this function is relevant for both
7068:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         internal trigger (SW start) and external trigger:
7069:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - If ADC trigger has been set to software start, ADC conversion
7070:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           starts immediately.
7071:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - If ADC trigger has been set to external trigger, ADC conversion
7072:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           will start at next trigger event (on the selected trigger edge)
7073:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           following the ADC start conversion command.
